		<div class="entry" id="entry-6a00d8341c630a53ef017d3eac015b970c">
	
	<h1 class="entry-header"><a href="http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/california-politics/2012/12/berman-sherman-congressional-race-sets-spending-record.html" rel="bookmark" title="Berman-Sherman House race sets spending record">Berman-Sherman House race sets spending record</a></h1>
	
	
        <div class="social-media-container">
    <div class="time">
        December 10, 2012&nbsp;|&nbsp;<span style="color:#8b0412;font-size:130%"> 4:39</span>
        <span style="color:#8b0412">pm</span>
    </div>
    <div class="social_media_container">

        <div style="float:left; width:100px; height:22px; margin-right:10px; margin-top:4px;">
            <span style="float:left; margin-right:5px;" st_url="http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/california-politics/2012/12/berman-sherman-congressional-race-sets-spending-record.html" st_title="Berman-Sherman House race sets spending record" st_summary="Democratic rivals Howard Berman and Brad Sherman set a California candidate spending record with their race for a San Fernando Valley congressional district seat.  Sherman defeated Berman on Nov. 6.

" class="st_email"></span>

            <div class="print_page" onclick="window.print(); return false;"></div>

