		<div class="entry" id="entry-6a00d8341c630a53ef017d3d60acb1970c">
	
	<h1 class="entry-header"><a href="http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/california-politics/2012/11/california-jerry-brown-democrats-big-winners-election.html" rel="bookmark" title="Jerry Brown, California Democrats appear to be big winners in election">Jerry Brown, California Democrats appear to be big winners in election</a></h1>
	
	
        <div class="social-media-container">
    <div class="time">
        November  7, 2012&nbsp;|&nbsp;<span style="color:#8b0412;font-size:130%"> 5:49</span>
        <span style="color:#8b0412">am</span>
    </div>
    <div class="social_media_container">

        <div style="float:left; width:100px; height:22px; margin-right:10px; margin-top:4px;">
            <span style="float:left; margin-right:5px;" st_url="http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/california-politics/2012/11/california-jerry-brown-democrats-big-winners-election.html" st_title="Jerry Brown, California Democrats appear to be big winners in election" st_summary="Gov. Jerry Brown’s $6-billion-a-year tax initiative to rescue California schools and the state's finances appeared to squeak by with a victory." class="st_email"></span>

            <div class="print_page" onclick="window.print(); return false;"></div>

            <span class="nextgen-font-size"></span>

            <a style="float:left;" href="#" onclick="font_size('up'); return false;" rel="nofollow">
                <img src="http://www.latimes.com/hive/images/icons/atools-uparrow.gif" alt="increase text size" class="arrow-img" />
            </a>

