atimesblogs.latimes.com/california-politics/legislature/" rel="section">Legislature</a>, <a href="http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/california-politics/proposition-30/" rel="section">Proposition 30</a>, <a href="http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/california-politics/redistricting/" rel="section">redistricting</a>, <a href="http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/california-politics/republican-party/" rel="section">Republican Party</a>, <a href="http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/california-politics/steve-cooley/" rel="section">Steve Cooley</a>, <a href="http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/california-politics/taxes/" rel="section">taxes</a>, <a href="http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/california-politics/tony-strickland/" rel="section">Tony Strickland</a>, <a href="http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/california-politics/transportation/" rel="section">transportation</a>


