	<h1 class="entry-header"><a href="http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/california-politics/2012/11/berman-sherman-battle-enters-final-weekend.html" rel="bookmark" title="Berman-Sherman battle enters final weekend">Berman-Sherman battle enters final weekend</a></h1>
	
	
        <div class="social-media-container">
    <div class="time">
        November  3, 2012&nbsp;|&nbsp;<span style="color:#8b0412;font-size:130%"> 6:00</span>
        <span style="color:#8b0412">am</span>
    </div>
    <div class="social_media_container">

        <div style="float:left; width:100px; height:22px; margin-right:10px; margin-top:4px;">
