		<div class="entry" id="entry-6a00d8341c630a53ef017ee494dbf3970d">
	
	<h1 class="entry-header"><a href="http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/california-politics/2012/10/democrats-mailer.html" rel="bookmark" title="L.A. Democrats decry outside group's mailer slamming elected officials">L.A. Democrats decry outside group's mailer slamming elected officials</a></h1>
	
	
        <div class="social-media-container">
    <div class="time">
        October 30, 2012&nbsp;|&nbsp;<span style="color:#8b0412;font-size:130%"> 2:34</span>
        <span style="color:#8b0412">pm</span>
