            <span style="float:left; margin-right:5px;" st_url="http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/california-politics/2012/10/democrats-mailer.html" st_title="L.A. Democrats decry outside group's mailer slamming elected officials" st_summary="The chair of the Los Angeles County Democratic Party has criticized an outside group's mailer in the bruising  election battle between  Democratic Reps. Brad Sherman and Howard Berman in the San Fernando Valley.  Californians for Integrity in Government send a mailer to Republican voters that slammed three liberal Democratic officeholders who are backing Berman." class="st_email"></span>

