<p><a href="http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/california-politics/2012/10/gov-jerry-brown-to-hit-the-road-for-prop-30.html" rel="bookmark" title="Gov. Jerry Brown to hit the road for Prop. 30">Gov. Jerry Brown to hit the road for Prop. 30</a></p>
<p><a href="http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/california-politics/2012/10/jerry-brown-back-on-the-stump-reaches-out-to-young-voters.html" rel="bookmark" title="Jerry Brown, back on the stump, reaches out to young voters">Jerry Brown, back on the stump, reaches out to young voters</a></p>
<p>
<a href="http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/california-politics/2012/10/california-voter-hotline-wrong-information-registration-deadline.html" rel="bookmark" title="State hotline gave wrong information on voter registration deadline">State hotline gave wrong information on voter registration deadline</a></p>
<p>--Jean Merl</p>
