	<h1 class="entry-header"><a href="http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/california-politics/2012/10/congessmen-sherman-berman-continue-to-rake-in-campaign-cash.html" rel="bookmark" title="Reps. Berman, Sherman continue to rake in campaign cash">Reps. Berman, Sherman continue to rake in campaign cash</a></h1>
	
	
        <div class="social-media-container">
    <div class="time">
        October 16, 2012&nbsp;|&nbsp;<span style="color:#8b0412;font-size:130%">11:43</span>
        <span style="color:#8b0412">am</span>
    </div>
    <div class="social_media_container">

